         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Melbourne bot. Museum, ¶ 1/8/73 ¶ Sir ¶  ¶ I have the honor to return herewith the account for salary (including allowance for houserent) signed by me. I further beg to submit the paysheet for the rem...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">73.08.01</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To James Francis</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">D73/9914, unit 1022, VPRS 3991/P inward registered correspondence, VA 475 Chief Secretary's Department, Public Record Office, Victoria.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">Melbourne bot. Museum,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">1/8/73</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Sir</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I have the honor to return herewith the account for salary (including allowance for houserent) signed by me. I further beg to submit the paysheet for the remuneration of the assistant and attendent<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>assistant<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">and</seg>
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>attendent<seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">
                           <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>both underlined in pencil</seg>. Marginal<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>note by unknown<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>against 'assistant',<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>'9/- per diem',<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>and against 'attendent',<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>'7/6' per<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>diem'.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>of my Department for the month of July, and also some incidental accounts, concerning the service of that month, trusting that they will meet with your favorable consideration and approval.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn1" n="2">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>See also M to J. Francis, 4 August 1873.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>MS annotation, on 6 August 1873, by Francis: 'Dr Mueller must recognize that £<seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                           <hi rend="underline">300</hi>
                        </seg>
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>in the 1873/4 Estimates is for collecting Botanical specimens clerical assistance &amp;c and that the [present] […] will<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>not permit of two assistants and<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>therefore one must be dispensed with as no Supplementary Estimate will be asked for'.</p>
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>MS annotation, the same day, by M: 'Baron von Muellers respectful reply is attached',<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>i.e.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>M to J. Francis, 6 August 1871.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I have the honor to be, Sir, your obedient servant</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Ferd. von Mueller</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">The honorable the Chief Secretary</p>
         </div>
